MNIST CAPTCHA
This starter notebook focuses on solving the MNIST CAPTCHA problem. The goal is to design a system that recognizes the digits and the operator from an "AB ± CD" image in order to calculate the final result. The notebook provides the basic steps: library imports, downloading the MNIST dataset, and a simple classifier, so you can continue with your own implementations.
